																If you are not the intended recipient, any
																dissemination, use, review, distribution, printing or
																copying of the information contained in this email
																message and/or attachments to it are strictly
																prohibited. If you have received this communication in
																error, please notify us by reply e-mail or telephone and
																immediately and permanently delete the message and any
																attachments. Thank you.
															</p>
														</div>
													</td>
												</tr>
											</table>
										</td>
									</tr>
